textBeforeTable: Here's a rundown of the top five, plus IU, UK and U of L players. The full rankings can be found online at www.CBSSports.com/collegebasketball. Who's who in hoops Who's who in hoops - Steve Jones CBS' Jeff Goodman wrote that "Zeller can do it all - score in the post, on the perimeter, run the court, defend and block shots. He's the odds-on favorite for National Player of the Year honors and also the No. 1 pick in June's NBA draft." Murray State guard Isaiah Canaan is No. 4 and Kentucky freshman Nerlens Noel No. 5. Indiana University sophomore center Cody Zeller is No. 1 in CBSSports.com's preseason rankings of the top 100 players in college basketball - a list on which IU, the University of Kentucky and University of Louisville are well-represented.
